Class ExperimentalServiceGrpc

java.lang.Object
com.authzed.api.v1.ExperimentalServiceGrpc
public final class ExperimentalServiceGrpc extends Object
 ExperimentalService exposes a number of APIs that are currently being
 prototyped and tested for future inclusion in the stable API.
